{"tid":2243130,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陸頌雄：特區政府官員在創科方面應向深圳學習","createTime":"2020-10-14T13:31:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-14T16:16:22.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"943c101d7bc059ceba412bd5c5a9ea442c084072","tid":2243130,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T13:31:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1554759-20201014.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1554759-20201014.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=LQfwTnO421PZAKP%2FvRgyiXlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=7889c0d5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1554759-20201014.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=76d5db1e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1554759-20201014.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n國家主席習近平在深圳出席經濟特區建立40周年慶祝大會，並發表講話。工聯會立法會議員陸頌雄表示，習近平的講話對香港有啟發性，特區政府官員在創科方面應向深圳學習，急起直追，不能只依賴金融、地產等傳統優勢產業，政府亦應加快與內地溝通，例如在教育和醫療提供支援和配套措施，方便年青人北上發展。<br />\n<br />\n議員郭偉強表示，香港是彈丸之地，近年陷於政治爭拗，如青年人想進一步發展，大灣區是必然之選。<br />\n<br />\n另一名議員麥美娟表示，當局應與廣東省政府商討，盡快推出港康碼，以恢復跨境人流物流及經濟。"},{"pid":"50665f7c064e12b37d8f3bf2e1f5c536545af1a8","tid":2243130,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T13:33:20.000Z","msg":"無私隱當然乜都好咁<br />\n<br />\n仲有，青島已經爆發緊，你想死就開關啦"},{"pid":"46680905ff44f62ba9627038c2efbc49f2765de1","tid":2243130,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T13:34:36.000Z","msg":"咁唔知要dump幾多錢落去了..."},{"pid":"f88454ec2ca03961b5e2beb44d2d540d24acc22f","tid":2243130,"uid":28202,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T13:36:18.000Z","msg":"宣傳機器開始開動，近個星期係咁踩香港同香港年青人，其實係香港根本老中青都唔妥你共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c70136a9b30d140da6c06bc9cc1a75f2eb71f09","tid":2243130,"uid":288913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{